Question: Do you think standard tests accurately assess student abilities?
Answer:
standard test can assess student abilities in some aspects but far from all.

first. it test your abilities based on your performance in the exam. specifically. your scores of the exam. so it only reflect your performance in short time. but many students are good at solving problem with flexible time.

second. it only test your study abilities. but study is only a  small part of people.s abiliyies.